---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About | Joshua Phillips"
	description="My experience, education, and skills."
>
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-text-main mb-8">About Me</h1>

		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Background</h2>
			<div class="text-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4">
				<p>As an early career Data Scientist, 
				I am passionate about applying my skills and knowledge in machine learning, data analysis, and data visualization to solving real-world problems.</p>
				<p>I recently completed a Masters of Data Science from the University of New South Wales, graduating with Excellence. 
				Prior to that I completed a conjoint undergraduate degree majoring in Statistics, Computer Science, and Mathematics.</p>

				<p>Beyond data I am a passionate tennis player and frequently made miserable by the New York Mets.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Experience</h2>
			<div class="bg-bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg shadow-card">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-main mb-2">Data Scientist</h3>
				<p class="text-text-secondary mb-2">Orbis Diagnostics 2025 - </p>
				
				<p class="text-text-secondary mb-2">
					My primary duties at Orbis have been the analysis of large-scale experimental data to further our goals in research and development. I have supported this work with the creation of **Hippa and ISO compliant databases** both for day-to-day operational work as well as clinical study data collection.
				</p>
				<p class="text-text-secondary mb-2">
					In addition to this, I have performed additional tasks as needed by Orbis, including:
				</p>
				<ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-6 space-y-3 text-text-secondary mb-2">
					<li>
						Leading a project that reduced total production time by 30%, freeing up staff capacity to focus on higher-value, non-production tasks.
					</li>
					<li>
						Reviewing international regulations on software and data management in diagnostics, ultimately enabling me to **author standard operating procedures** to ensure ongoing ISO and regulatory compliance. Compliance in these areas is crucial to our ongoing **FDA submission process**.
					</li>
					<li>
						Performing internal audits to ensure ISO 13485 compliance.
					</li>
					<li>
						Conducting day-to-day hands-on production tasks to enable research. In support of this, I designed and produced multiple tools which reduced 'sticking points' in workflows.
					</li>
				</ul>

			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Education</h2>
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="bg-bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg shadow-card">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-main mb-2">Master of Data Science</h3>
					<p class="text-text-secondary mb-2">University of New South Wales</p>
					<p class="text-text-tertiary text-sm">2024 - 2025</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg shadow-card">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-main mb-2">Bachelor of Science</h3>
					<p class="text-text-secondary mb-2">University of Auckland</p>
					<p class="text-text-tertiary text-sm">2020 - 2023</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-12">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Skills & Technologies</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
				<div class="bg-bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg shadow-card">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-main mb-3">Languages</h3>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<span class="bg-border-main text-text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">Python</span>
						<span class="bg-border-main text-text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">R</span>
						<span class="bg-border-main text-text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">GIT</span>
					</div>
				</div>


				<div class="bg-bg-secondary p-6 rounded-lg shadow-card">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-main mb-3">Regulatory Compliance</h3>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
						<span class="bg-border-main text-text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">ISO 13485</span>
						<span class="bg-border-main text-text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">HIPAA</span>
						<span class="bg-border-main text-text-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm">Internal audits</span>
					</div>
